OL,3,CSearches continue at nature reserve
OL,4,Cfor missing teenage boy
OL,6,FSearches are continuing for a missing
OL,7,Fteenage boy who was last seen swimming
OL,8,Fat a Hampshire nature reserve.
OL,10,FThe 15-year-old entered the water at
OL,11,FTestwood Lakes, near Totton, on
OL,12,FWednesday.
OL,14,FOfficers and a marine unit from
OL,15,FHampshire & Isle of Wight Police have
OL,16,Fbeen looking for him ever since.
OL,18,FThey've been supported by colleagues
OL,19,Fat Hampshire & Isle of Wight Fire &
OL,20,FRescue Service and Hampshire Search
OL,21,Fand Rescue.
