OL,3,CSearches continue at nature reserve
OL,4,Cfor missing teenage boy
OL,6,FA statement issued by police on Friday
OL,7,Fsaid that searches "continued until
OL,8,Flate into the evening yesterday
OL,9,F(Thursday) and resumed again first
OL,10,Fthing this morning".
OL,12,FThe force added the area continues to
OL,13,Fbe closed to the public, but that it
OL,14,Fwill "endeavour to provide further
OL,15,Fupdates as soon as we are able to".
OL,17,FThe boy's family are being supported
OL,18,Fby specially trained officers.
